return.description:
Returns one of the following:
   
    Variant Comparision Results
    
     
      
       value
       meaning
      
     
     
      
       VARCMP_LT
       left is less than
        right
       
      
      
       VARCMP_EQ
       left is equal to
        right
       
      
      
       VARCMP_GT
       left is greater than
        right
       
      
      
       VARCMP_NULL
       Either left,
        right or both are NULL
